.DT
domainlock
Discworld creator help
domainlock

.SH Name
.SI 5
domainlock - Lock a domain
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
domainlock <domain> off 
domainlock <domain> on 
domainlock list 
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command lets you see which domains are locked, and to change access
to a domain.  When locking a domain, you will be prompted for a reason
for closing the domain.
.EP

.SP 5 5
This command interfaces with /d/am/patrician/patrician.c.  Commands here
can be performed from that room as well.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
domainlock cwc off
domainlock am on
.EI

.SI 5
>domainlock list
.EI

.SI 10
The domain status is:
Am is currently open for applications.
Cwc is currently closed for applications.
Klatch is currently closed for applications.
Liaison is currently closed for applications.
Playtesters is currently closed for applications.
Ram is currently open for applications.
Sur is currently open for applications.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
employ, dismiss
.EP
